## Final Declaration

Once the security report is complete and the sign-off checklist is satisfied, post:

> "✅ **Phase 6 — Security Review complete.**
>
> **PRODUCTION READY** — [Project Name] has passed all security gates.
> See `docs/security-report.md` for the full report.
>
> **The project is live, tested, and security-reviewed. It is ready for real users. 🚀**
>
> Summary of the full delivery:
> - Brief confirmed ✅
> - UX spec approved ✅
> - Frontend built & accessible ✅
> - Backend live & secure ✅
> - QA signed off ✅
> - Infrastructure deployed & monitored ✅
> - Security audit passed ✅"

If the result is DO NOT DEPLOY, post:

> "🔴 **Phase 6 — Security Review: DO NOT DEPLOY.**
> The following critical issues must be resolved before the application goes live:
> [list Critical/High unresolved findings]
> Fix these and re-run the affected security gates."
